sub_title: PhD Candidate at Delft University of Technology | Geophysicist  | Electrical Engineer
summary: Ph.D. Candidate at Delft University of Technology (TU Delft) in the section of Applied Geophysics and Petrophysics; Master of Science of the IDEA league joint master’s program in Applied Geophysics at TU Delft, ETH Zurich, and RWTH Aachen; Bachelor of Science in Electronics Engineer and Earth Sciences from Universidad of Los Andes, Colombia. I have a strong theoretical background in numerical modeling, computational geophysics, inverse theory, machine learning, and signal processing. Excellent competencies in software programming and scientific computing; always looking forward to learning, cooperating, and developing new skills.
